definition: ox/cow/bull/CL:條|条[tiao2],頭|头[tou2]/newton (abbr. for 牛頓|牛顿[niu2 dun4])/(slang) awesome
saliva/sweat/a ferry crossing/a ford (river crossing)/abbr. for Tianjin 天津

sentences.english: The 5th edition Oxford English-Chinese Dictionary is much thicker than the 4th one.
sentences.chinese: 第五版牛津英汉双解词典比第四版厚得多。

sentences.english: The busiest shopping area is Oxford Street, where famous large department stores are located.
sentences.chinese: 最繁华的购物区是拥有著名大百货公司的牛津街。

sentences.english: For Oxford, the decision to go online-only would make a great deal of economic sense.
sentences.chinese: 对牛津来说，只出网络版将更合符经济效益。

sentences.english: He went to Queen's College at Oxford, England.
sentences.chinese: 他去了英国牛津大学皇后学院。

sentences.english: If you bought this tea-set in Oxford Street, it would cost you ￡14 at least!
sentences.chinese: 如果你在牛津街买这套茶具，你至少得化14英镑。

sentences.english: He sauntered along Oxford Street looking at the shopwindows.
sentences.chinese: 他沿牛津街漫步观看商店的橱窗。

sentences.english: His address is 329 Oxford Street, Belmont.
sentences.chinese: 他的地址是贝尔蒙特牛津街329号。

sentences.english: Cathy YE Tissue Engineering and Bioprocessing, Oxford, lecturer.
sentences.chinese: 牛津大学，组织工程与生物加工中心，讲师。

sentences.english: 1214 - University of Oxford receives its charter.
sentences.chinese: 1214年的今天，牛津大学获得特许执照。

sentences.english: He studied English while staying at Oxford Thrangu House.
sentences.chinese: 随后，他前住英国创古牛津屋学习英语。

sentences.english: I bumped into an old flame of yours in Oxford on Saturday.
sentences.chinese: 星期六我在牛津碰到了你的一个老相好。

sentences.english: However, she decided against it and continued at Oxford.
sentences.chinese: 但是她决心对抗，同时继续在牛津读书。

sentences.english: I played on the Oxford University varsity basketball team.
sentences.chinese: 我当时是牛津大学篮球队的成员。

sentences.english: He is currently visiting professor of planning at Oxford Brookes University.
sentences.chinese: 他现任牛津布鲁克斯大学的城市规划客座教授。

sentences.english: Blenheim Palace in Woodstock, Oxfordshire. (Jason Hawkes)
sentences.chinese: 布莱尼姆宫，伍德斯托克，牛津郡。

sentences.english: Oxford Landing was established in 1958 on the bands of the majestic murray river in south Australia.
sentences.chinese: 牛津园于1958年在南澳宏伟的墨累河岸推出。
